<br>
The idea of &quot;emotional amnesia&quot; as well as total amnesia is really good! Maybe Saphire's dad knew there was a potential for memory loss/block but didn't realize the sociopathic results of the HAE project as well. So while all the facts could be poured back into Saphire's head, the emotions and morality couldn't.<br>
<br>
Like amnesia, Saphire would get &quot;emotional flashbacks&quot; at certain poignant moments. Noa may try to help her get back to emotional high ground.<br>
<br>
